{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>\u201c<strong>Slay the Spire</strong> Meets <strong>Into the Breach</strong>! Great New Deckbuilder Just Landed!\u201d</i> - <strong>Haelian</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;One Of The Best Grid-Based Roguelike Deckbuilders I've Seen So Far&quot;</i> - <strong>Wanderbot</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;AWESOME Turn-Based Tactics Roguelike Deckbuilder!!&quot;</i> - <strong>Retromation</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/banner_tactics.png?t=1729034419\" />Choose your heroes that will fight to rid this world of corrupted Tendryll.  In order to survive, your heroes must work together and coordinate their unique abilities.  You will encounter deadly enemies, dangerous traps, and perilous environmental hazards that hex your cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/biomes.gif?t=1729034419\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/banner_advanced_movements.png?t=1729034419\" />Each hero has its own move deck and draws a guaranteed move card each turn - allowing your heroes to always be in the fight. Dedicated map nodes let you swap in new move cards to maintain a balanced move deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alongside their move decks, heroes also have unique attacks and skills that give them powerful ways to reposition themselves and others.  You will knock enemies back into walls, teleport to random locations to gain an energy advantage, or throw allies and enemies across the battlefield - dealing heavy damage around where they land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/banner_runes_and_anomalies.png?t=1729034419\" />Double your block, gain Invisibility, or play your card twice - every card can potentially be improved with impactful runes like these.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you\u2019re feeling bold or desperate, shops and black markets offer risky anomalies that reward you with items for free - if you don\u2019t pay with your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/banner_runes_and_anomalies_600x192.png?t=1729034419\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/banner_forge_your_path.png?t=1729034419\" />Survival requires difficult choices.  Along your journey, your heroes will find card-altering runes, unique movement cards, and class-defining relics.  Will your heroes take the greedy path to perfect their archetypes, or will they take a safer path, restoring their health with the hope of surviving another battle?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/choices.gif?t=1729034419\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 170+ cards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 115+ relics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 3+ heroes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 3 acts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 5+ bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 35+ unique encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 20+ combat modifiers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 30+ bounties that unlock heroes, relics, and potions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 14+ runes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 10 ascension levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Full Steam Deck support (pending Steam validation)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/banner_wishlist_now.png?t=1729034419\" />Wishlist to get updated when we release. Every wishlist helps our development of the game! </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Adversity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1915780/84447ee61a427004ea25e7bb080f621979dcae86.jpg"},{"name":"Altered","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1915780/9ecc26991a4456db81455387f8d65ed7fe7dd02c.jpg"},{"name":"Unphased","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1915780/6779b012ccf27fbb8f840d6ff6df60e8834a0ffd.jpg"},{"name":"Ascend","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1915780/c516ebae1fed4214a5de2251fdc3c2d1c0cebc86.jpg"},{"name":"Ascension 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1915780/ad6bdb8189d9e4cc3a3721c8461dbb91f0f1335e.jpg"},{"name":"Ascension 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1915780/b3b84ead7971e0a7aa05ee493b987a223b944474.jpg"},{"name":"Ascension 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1915780/5ca428d33ff93cf62bf991a634222bd614f254b9.jpg"},{"name":"Ascension 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1915780/d0b90d440b77f3e9ab1872ab24bf87d0ece2fa57.jpg"},{"name":"Ascension 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1915780/5733d34cecd04edfd7a26cf1874e3285b588a6e1.jpg"},{"name":"Ascension 6","path":"https://cdn.a